2. Degradation or Total Loss of Services or Functions
(a) Inability to provide ATM services or to execute ATM functions:
(1) inability to provide air traffic services or to execute air traffic services functions;

(b) Degradation or total loss of services or functions
(1) Loss or failure of communication between:
(i) aerodrome, vehicle or other ground personnel and air traffic services unit or apron management service unit;
